rows.dataScript:
client.act("Search the current Amazon stock price using AMZN.")
client.act("Switch the graph to viewing the 6M tab instead of the 1D tab.")
result = client.act("Return a bounding box of the price graph.")
return { "type": "crop", "box": result.response }

client.act("Type 'Tell me about AMZN' in the search bar")
client.act("Click on the black up arrow in the bottom right of the text box")
